entityDefinitions.name: Name

locallyDefinedProperties.description: A name given to an individual at birth, baptism, or during another naming ceremony, or through legal change.
The name borne in common by members of a family.

entityDefinitions.description: The set of elements that comprise a person's legal name.

entityDefinitions.name: Parent
entityDefinitions.description: This entity represents an individual for whom instruction, services, and/or care are provided in an early childhood, elementary, or secondary educational program under the jurisdiction of a school, education agency or other institution or program. A student is a person who has been enrolled in a school or other educational institution.

entityDefinitions.name: ParentAddress

locallyDefinedProperties.description: The name of the city in which an address is located.

entityDefinitions.description: The set of elements that describes an address, including the street address, city, state, and ZIP code.

entityDefinitions.name: ParentStudentSchoolAssociation
entityDefinitions.description: The students association with the parent.

entityDefinitions.name: School
entityDefinitions.description: This entity represents an educational organization that includes staff and students who participate in classes and educational activity groups.

entityDefinitions.name: SchoolAddress

locallyDefinedProperties.description: The name of the city in which an address is located.

entityDefinitions.description: The set of elements that describes an address, including the street address, city, state, and ZIP code.

entityDefinitions.name: Staff
entityDefinitions.description: same name as a core domain entity

locallyDefinedProperties.description: The name of the city in which an address is located.

entityDefinitions.name: StaffStudentSchoolAssociation
entityDefinitions.description: The students under the instruction of the staff member

entityDefinitions.name: Student
entityDefinitions.description: This entity represents an individual for whom instruction, services, and/or care are provided in an early childhood, elementary, or secondary educational program under the jurisdiction of a school, education agency or other institution or program. A student is a person who has been enrolled in a school or other educational institution.

entityDefinitions.name: StudentAddress

locallyDefinedProperties.description: The name of the city in which an address is located.

entityDefinitions.description: The set of elements that describes an address, including the street address, city, state, and ZIP code.

entityDefinitions.name: StudentSchoolAssociation
entityDefinitions.description: This association represents the School in which a student is enrolled. The semantics of enrollment may differ slightly by state. Non-enrollment relationships between a student and an education organization may be described using the StudentEducationOrganizationAssociation.
